definition: entity/substance/thing that has a material existence (as opposed to a conceptual, virtual or online existence)/the real thing (as opposed to an image or model of it)
brick and mortar business/physical (rather than online) retail store

sentences.english: The solid mineralizing model for a underground gold mine is researched on the basis of orebody block as a unit.
